      "originalText": "⚠️ OPTIMISM IS DANGEROUS\nStale data · Wasted bandwidth · Pre-auth leaks · State mutation · Memory bloat\nMitigate: read-only prefetch · post-auth gate · delta sync · Cache-Control: no-store on logout",
